Path: godot/tutorials/platform/ios/plugins_for_ios.rst
Summary: This document explains how to use plugins for iOS development in Godot.

This document is outdated.

This document explains how to use plugins for iOS development in Godot. It covers the process of integrating third-party libraries and custom code into your Godot project for iOS deployment. The focus is on how to structure your plugin, handle native code compilation, and ensure compatibility with the Godot build system for iOS.
