Summary: This section describes the Game Center plugin for iOS, detailing its available methods and pending event interface.

The Game Center API is available through the GameCenter singleton. It has the following methods:

Method: authenticate() → Error
Method: is_authenticated() → bool
Method: post_score(score: Variant) → Error
Method: award_achievement(params: Variant) → Error
Method: reset_achievements() → void
Method: request_achievements() → void
Method: request_achievement_descriptions() → void
Method: show_game_center(params: Variant) → Error
Method: request_identity_verification_signature() → Error

And the pending events interface:

Method: get_pending_event_count() → int
Method: pop_pending_event() → Variant
---CHUNK---
